description:
This course is meant to help immigrants who are new to the U.S. workplace to understand how they can become leaders within their workplace and continue to grow their career.

This course is made up of Powerpoint presentations that include recorded audio to deliver the course strategies, along with video interviews and follow up assignments. This course will be an exercise in self-evaluation and planning, goal setting, and understanding different personalities and communication styles that you will encounter within the U.S. workplace. You definitely will learn something new about yourself and your colleagues!

Please join me on a career development journey. I am happy to answer your questions within the discussion forum and welcome your feedback!
title: Leadership Strategies for Immigrants in the U.S. Workplace
